      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence with this showroom-quality masterpiece. Meticulously maintained and presented in truly impeccable condition, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior cabin, reflects a history of uncompromising care. This is more than a pre-owned vehicle; it is a testament to superior engineering preserved in its finest form.",
